'''I Came, I Saw, I Conquered''' is an [[Achievement]] in the category ''[[Meetings in Outrealm: Series I]]''. To complete this achievement, the player needs to collect 5 [[Local Specialty|regional specialties]] in another player's world.

==Trivia==
* "I Came, I Saw, I Conquered" is the English translation of ''{{w|veni, vidi, vici}}'' &mdash; a Latin phrase that is popularly attributed to {{w|Julius Caesar}}.
